   comment form‘s email field. Specific to the site from which it is set.
   This cookie mirrors one set by the core WordPress software for
   commenting purposes.
   comment_author_url_{HASH} Remembers the value entered into the comment
   form‘s URL field. Specific to the site from which it is set. This
   cookie mirrors one set by the core WordPress software for commenting
   purposes

