   Cookie Purpose
   ads Tracks if a visitor has clicked an ad before.
   lr_nw Counts and tracks pageviews on Longreads.com. Used to determine
   whether or not to show our Membership popup message.
   wordpress_eli Reduces the display of ads for repeat visitors.

